OL,5, An executive at a centuries-old        
OL,6, investment firm has accused the media  
OL,7, of "corporate bullying" after it       
OL,8, changed its name to Abrdn.             
OL,10,FThe asset manager rebranded from       
OL,11,FStandard Life Aberdeen three years ago,
OL,12,Fshortening its name and dropping the   
OL,13,Fvowels.                                
OL,15,FChief investment officer Peter Branner 
OL,16,Fcomplained the press was making        
OL,17,F"childish" jokes about the change.     
OL,19,FHe said it would be unethical to treat 
OL,20,Fan individual in the same way.         
